LogFile.FinalText: The resemblance is striking. This is how many people see Denmark's two princesses. There are many similarities between Mary and Marie but just as many differences, if not more. They are both from abroad, neither of them was born a royalty, and each has found their prince of Denmark. Mary is married to crown prince Frederik and Marie is married to prince Joachim. Also, their names and appearance are very similar. They are both gorgeous with long, dark hair and big, brown eyes. But in spite the many similarities, Mary and Marie are also to individuals who have lived and are living different lives, and it has affected their values and personalities.
